## Multi-flavor support
  # Recipe
  flavor_array attrib (immarray)
    flavor tags => percentage
  get_flavor_percentage
  flavor_percentage 
    should be _flavor_array total if present
    else should be required

  # Role::Calc
  if flavor_array is present, calculate each
  else calc flavor_percentage
  sanity check against flavor_percentage

  # frontend ->
  Flavor cmd subject should be expanded to allow
    'set total <%>' 
    'set tag <tag> <%>'
    'add flavor <tag> <%>'
    'del flavor <tag> <%>'
  Template needs appropriate adjustment
